    <para styleclass="Figure E" style="margin-bottom:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;">图 &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER5=2%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER=1%&gt; </text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">轴配置 1</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Figure E" style="margin-bottom:0px;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Figure E" style="margin-bottom:0px;"><image src="Fig 2.2_Chp 5.png" scale="60.00%" width="447" height="594" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Figure E" style="margin-bottom:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;">图 &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER5=2%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER%&gt; </text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">轴配置 2</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Figure E" style="margin-bottom:0px;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;"><text style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold;">伺服电机耦合</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">电机轴和滚珠丝杠通过电机联轴器连接。联轴器由联轴器法兰和扁平弹簧组成。当夹紧螺钉拧紧时，联轴器法兰变形，通过摩擦力将电机轴和滚珠丝杠连接起来。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><image src="Fig 2.3_Chp 5.png" scale="60.00%" width="443" height="259" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
